data.description: The two-story, 3 bed/2.5 bath Yale plan is features an open floor plan and gorgeous natural light! The great room and dining nook flow together to create one large area. The stunning kitchen features wrap-around counters, energy-efficient appliances and overlooks the great room. A spacious loft that acts as a flex area. The master suite includes a generously-sized bedroom with large window, a private bath and a walk-in closet. This home includes over $25,000 in upgrades!
